<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>2048小游戏</title>
    <!-- 风格和2048游戏呼应，保持视觉统一 -->
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #FFF8E7; /* 和2048游戏背景一致 */
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #8B6914; /* 2048主色调 */
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 3.5rem);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        /* 游戏入口按钮（和2048按钮风格一致的3D效果） */
        .play-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 20px 60px;
            background-color: #CD853F; /* 2048 accent色 */
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 5vw, 2rem);
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 0 0 #8B6914; /* 3D阴影 */
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .play-btn:active {
            transform: translateY(6px);
            box-shadow: none; /* 按下时的3D反馈 */
        }
        .tips {
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 3vw, 1.1rem);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>2048 小游戏</h1>
        <!-- 核心修改：跳转链接改为 2048_game.html -->
        <a href="2048_game.html" class="play-btn">开始游戏</a>
        <!-- 简单的操作提示，和游戏内提示一致 -->
        <div class="tips">
            <p>🖥️ 电脑：方向键控制棋子移动</p>
            <p>📱 手机：滑动屏幕控制方向</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
